---
group_count: 17
atr1_unknown: 0
entries:
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk000:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 338
      - text: "你變強了呢……真的變強了。\n米法的祈福也應該更能派上用場才是。"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk010:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 332
      - text: "現在的你一定能夠拯救海拉魯……\n以及在城裡等待的公主殿下……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk100:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 208
      - text: "……你果然很厲害呢。\n當時我連反擊的機會都沒有，就被打倒了……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk110:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 249
      - text: "我相信現在的你，一定不會輸給加儂。\n我的祈福也會助你一臂之力……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk120:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 184
      - text: "所以……\n請你拯救那個人吧……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk200:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 185
      - text: 如果你去了卓拉領地，請代我轉達。
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk210:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 129
      - text: "告訴父王「我很抱歉」……\n"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk220:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 125
      - text: 告訴希多「好好加油」……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk230:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 256
      - text: "然後……有機會再替我轉告公主殿下，\n「好想再跟您多聊一些」……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk240:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 191
      - text: "還有……\n不，沒事了……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk300:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 166
      - text: "……林克，\n倘若……你在某處……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk310:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 133
      - text: 找到我的日記……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk320:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 125
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 100
      - text: 你絕對不能看喔！
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk330:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 224
      - text: "啊……抱歉，我太大聲了……\n可是……算我拜託你……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk400:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 204
      - text: "……林克，\n你還記得我們一起擊退怪物時的事嗎？"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk410:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 269
      - text: "當領地的人因為雷獸山上的萊尼爾\n而恐懼不已時，你出現了……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk420:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 112
      - text: 我們兩個一起戰鬥……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk430:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 115
      - text: 你是不是……不記得了？
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk500:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 238
      - text: "林克，我問你……100年前在領地的回憶，\n你還記得多少？"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk510:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 259
      - text: "卓拉鎧甲穿起來正好合身的理由，\n你也忘記了嗎……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk520:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 309
      - text: "很多事情我都希望你能回想起來，\n但如果你回想不起來，那也沒辦法……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk530:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 182
      - text: 可是……我不會忘記的……
